 \sum_{k=0}^\infty\frac{(-1)^k}{\sqrt {k+1}}\,\cdot\,\sum_{k=0}^\infty\frac{(-1)^k}{\sqrt {k+1}}=\sum_{n=0}^\infty\left(\sum_{k=0}^n\frac{(-1)^k}{\sqrt {k+1}}\,\frac{(-1)^{n-k}}{\sqrt{n+1- k}}\right)\\=\sum_{n=1}^\infty\,(-1)^n\sum_{k=0}^n\frac1{\sqrt{(k+1)(n+1-k)}} 
